# The Lylods Group Laravel Platform

# PHASE 7

# Enterprise Digital Asset Management (DAM)

---

# Executive Summary

The public website, CMS foundation and SEO architecture have now reached production maturity.

The next strategic objective is to eliminate every remaining hardcoded media asset throughout the platform and replace them with a centralized Digital Asset Management (DAM) system.

This is no longer an image upload feature.

This is the creation of an enterprise media platform that becomes the single source of truth for every digital asset used throughout The Lylods Group ecosystem.

Upon completion, administrators should never need developer assistance to replace logos, hero images, documents or downloadable resources.

---

# Vision

Build an enterprise-grade Digital Asset Management System that allows every visual and downloadable asset across the platform to be centrally managed, reused, optimized and secured.

Every image.

Every logo.

Every document.

Every download.

Every icon.

Every attachment.

Everything.

One system.

---

